Vaya, una granja, unas tierras...

153
00:10:03.920 --> 00:10:06.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Muy bonita la radio, Basilio.

154
00:10:06.080 --> 00:10:08.080 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
¿De dónde ha sacado todo este dinero?

155
00:10:08.920 --> 00:10:10.200 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
