156
00:10:10.280 --> 00:10:12.040 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
¿Tiene algún documento que lo pruebe?

157
00:10:13.240 --> 00:10:14.800 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
