250
00:16:07.120 --> 00:16:09.600 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
que es mucho más
de lo que podemos decir ahora.

251
00:16:14.120 --> 00:16:16.760 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Ojalá las cosas
hubieran sucedido de otra manera.

252
00:16:17.080 --> 00:16:19.440 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Nosotros
también podemos hacer que sucedan.

253
00:16:22.640 --> 00:16:25.920 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Sigo pensando
que a mi primera hija la llamaré Alba.

254
00:16:27.880 --> 00:16:29.160 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
No ha cambiado nada.

255
00:16:29.840 --> 00:16:31.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[Francisco] Para mí, nada.

256
00:16:32.160 --> 00:16:33.360 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Alba.

257
00:16:36.960 --> 00:16:38.160 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Me marcho.

258
00:16:38.720 --> 00:16:40.800 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Ya no tengo nada por lo que seguir aquí.

259
00:16:43.840 --> 00:16:45.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
¿Qué harás?

260
00:16:46.880 --> 00:16:48.200 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Aún no lo sé.

261
00:16:50.000 --> 00:16:52.120 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Prométeme que volveremos a vernos.

262
00:17:04.359 --> 00:17:05.720 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Francisco.

263
00:17:13.680 --> 00:17:14.760 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Gracias.

264
00:17:39.880 --> 00:17:40.880 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Alba.

265
00:17:51.760 --> 00:17:52.800 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[Lidia] Juan.

266
00:17:56.680 --> 00:17:58.160 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Creía que estabas muerto.

267
00:17:59.240 --> 00:18:01.080 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Creía que no iba a volver a verte nunca.

268
00:18:01.920 --> 00:18:03.320 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[Juan] Es largo de contar.

269
00:18:03.560 --> 00:18:06.400 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
