282
00:18:51.840 --> 00:18:52.840 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
¡Carlota!

283
00:18:52.920 --> 00:18:55.480 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Miguel, mi amor, estoy aquí.

284
00:18:55.600 --> 00:18:56.720 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
¿Me oyes?

285
